### Create new API key
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/apikey/create
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### List all API keys
GET http://localhost:3000/auth/apikeys
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Delete an API key (replace <id> with the API key ID)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/auth/apikey/<id>
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Create a new bucket
